<collectingCountry id="F3317652CA70FF9FCD8E397BF7C4FA0C" box="[2027,2114,1395,1424]" name="Japan" pageId="32" pageNumber="651">Japan</collectingCountry>
. The Japanese Weasel was previously considered a subspecies of the Siberian Weasel. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
